Generic single-database configuration.

Command	                                        Description
alembic init alembic	                        Initialize Alembic in your project
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Message"	Generate a new migration based on model changes
alembic upgrade head	                        Apply the latest migrations
alembic downgrade -1	                        Rollback the last migration
alembic downgrade <revision_id>	                Rollback to a specific migration
alembic history	                                Show migration history
alembic current	                                Show current migration version